title.rendered: 1000 PK – ProSafe Black Nitrile Powder Free Examination Gloves, MEDIUM

content.rendered:
The beaded cuff ensures easy donning and prevents roll down. Superior strength with excellent puncture resistance. Provides an alternative to those allergic to natural rubber. Powder Free to eliminate the risk of corn starch contamination. Excellent dexterity and feel. Chemical resistance to incidental splash exposure. Odour free.

Applications:

  • Mechanics
  • Automotive
  • Oil and Lubricant Handling
  • Materials Handling
  • Hairdressing
  • Tattooing
  • General Domestic

Available in S,M,L,XL sizes with 100 pairs per unit and 10 units per carton. Black Disposable and Powder Free.
